occurrenceRemarks: Scrub vegetation next to reservoir. Culms to 2cm diam., to 4m tall, erect at base, scandent and arching above. Internodes terete, 10-15 cm long, with a white, waxy band 1-1.5cm wide below each node. Branching infravaginal. Culm leaves persistent, abaxially glabrous, sheaths fused at base for 1.5-2cm.
